<h1>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</h1>

<% edit_count = Edit.pending.for_curating(@user).count %>
<p>The LCI App is holding <span style="font-size: x-large"><%= edit_count %> pending <%= 'edit'.pluralize(edit_count) %></span> waiting for your approval</p>

<p>Please log into the <%= link_to 'LCI App', login_url %> at your earliest opportunity,
  and attend to these at the <%= link_to 'Pending Edits page', curate_edits_url %></p>

<p>This email was automatically generated from the LCI App.
  If you feel you should not have received it please contact your LCI supervisor or replay to this email.</p>
</body>
</html>